			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "1) Go to 1353; 2; -773 and watch the dialog between the Captain and Templar. \r\n2) Then set roll amazing, sneak behind the Captain and steal the item in her inventory (stub name |Gith Shard|). \r\n3) Talk to the captain, and convince her to let you in to the templar (roll amazing will help)\r\nShe will walk to the door control and say the line, then turn hostile."
				},
